occurrence_remarks: The fossil is marked with the original Green River number and is often mistaken for the USNM number. That original Green River collection number is 52512.; This fossil-bearing rock has parts & counterparts with different original Green River numbers. Those numbers are: 52512 / 52609. All parts share the same USNM number: 572645.; Numbers associated with this fossil: 572645. 52512. 52609. 41679.
